{
  "video_id": "D9ZNpt6FVTY",
  "title": "Am I not human? A call for criminal justice reform | Marlon Peterson",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12842.0,
      "end_time": 14200.0,
      "text": "She wrote:"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14454.0,
      "end_time": 17100.0,
      "text": "\"When I become famous, I will tell everyone"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17250.0,
      "end_time": 19159.0,
      "text": "that I know a hero named Marlon Peterson.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20580.0,
      "end_time": 21758.0,
      "text": "Heroes rarely look like me."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22429.0,
      "end_time": 23854.0,
      "text": "In fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 23878.0,
      "end_time": 25558.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m what garbage looks like."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 26162.0,
      "end_time": 28965.0,
      "text": "No, not the most appealing way to open a talk"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 28990.0,
      "end_time": 30686.0,
      "text": "or start a conversation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 30711.0,
      "end_time": 34184.0,
      "text": "and perhaps you have some questions going through your head about that."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34208.0,
      "end_time": 36582.0,
      "text": "Why would this man say such a thing about himself?"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 36606.0,
      "end_time": 38790.0,
      "text": "What does he mean?"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 38103.0,
      "end_time": 42289.0,
      "text": "How can someone view him as a hero when he sees himself as garbage?"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 43730.0,
      "end_time": 46156.0,
      "text": "I believe we learn more from questions than we do from answers."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46180.0,
      "end_time": 48463.0,
      "text": "Because when we&#39;re questioning something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48487.0,
      "end_time": 51821.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re invested in taking in some sort of new information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51845.0,
      "end_time": 56820.0,
      "text": "or grappling with some sort of ignorance that makes us feel uncomfortable."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 56106.0,
      "end_time": 57812.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s why I&#39;m here:"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 57836.0,
      "end_time": 59370.0,
      "text": "to push us to question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 59395.0,
      "end_time": 61470.0,
      "text": "even when it makes us uncomfortable."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 62890.0,
      "end_time": 65320.0,
      "text": "My parents are from Trinidad and Tobago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 65560.0,
      "end_time": 67268.0,
      "text": "the southernmost island in the Caribbean."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 67293.0,
      "end_time": 70271.0,
      "text": "Trinidad is also home to the only acoustic instrument"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 70295.0,
      "end_time": 72165.0,
      "text": "invented in the 20th century:"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 72189.0,
      "end_time": 73472.0,
      "text": "the steel pan."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 74138.0,
      "end_time": 76531.0,
      "text": "Deriving from the African drums"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 76555.0,
      "end_time": 79832.0,
      "text": "and evolving from the genius of one of the ghettos in Trinidad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 79856.0,
      "end_time": 81542.0,
      "text": "a city called Laventille,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 81566.0,
      "end_time": 84542.0,
      "text": "and the disregard of the American military ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 85357.0,
      "end_time": 86653.0,
      "text": "Well, I should tell you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 86677.0,
      "end_time": 90440.0,
      "text": "America, during WWII, had military bases set up in Trinidad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 90680.0,
      "end_time": 91489.0,
      "text": "and when the war ended,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 91513.0,
      "end_time": 95490.0,
      "text": "they left the island littered with empty oil drums --"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 95730.0,
      "end_time": 96318.0,
      "text": "their trash."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 96767.0,
      "end_time": 101510.0,
      "text": "So people from Laventille repurposed the old drums left behind"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 101750.0,
      "end_time": 103278.0,
      "text": "into the full chromatic scale:"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 103302.0,
      "end_time": 104510.0,
      "text": "the steel pan."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 104907.0,
      "end_time": 109291.0,
      "text": "Playing music now from Beethoven to Bob Marley to 50 Cent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 109315.0,
      "end_time": 113553.0,
      "text": "those people literally made music out of garbage."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 114574.0,
      "end_time": 117730.0,
      "text": "Twelve days before my 20th birthday,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 117970.0,
      "end_time": 120967.0,
      "text": "I was arrested for my role in a violent robbery attempt"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 120992.0,
      "end_time": 122204.0,
      "text": "in lower Manhattan."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 122821.0,
      "end_time": 125170.0,
      "text": "While people were sitting in a coffee shop,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 126172.0,
      "end_time": 127539.0,
      "text": "four people were shot."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 129192.0,
      "end_time": 130519.0,
      "text": "Two were killed."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 131504.0,
      "end_time": 132945.0,
      "text": "Five of us were arrested."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 134330.0,
      "end_time": 136671.0,
      "text": "We were all the products of Trinidad and Tobago."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 136695.0,
      "end_time": 138603.0,
      "text": "We were the \"bad immigrants,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 138628.0,
      "end_time": 142664.0,
      "text": "or the \"anchor babies\" that Trump and millions of Americans easily malign."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 143715.0,
      "end_time": 146781.0,
      "text": "I was discarded, like waste material --"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 146805.0,
      "end_time": 149900.0,
      "text": "and justifiably so to many."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 149330.0,
      "end_time": 153410.0,
      "text": "I eventually served 10 years, two months and seven days of a prison sentence."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 154250.0,
      "end_time": 158922.0,
      "text": "I was sentenced to a decade of punishment in a correctional institution."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 159786.0,
      "end_time": 162330.0,
      "text": "I was sentenced to irrelevance --"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 162354.0,
      "end_time": 163997.0,
      "text": "the opposite of humanity."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 165690.0,
      "end_time": 166630.0,
      "text": "Interestingly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 166654.0,
      "end_time": 171677.0,
      "text": "it was during those years in prison that a series of letters redeemed me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 171701.0,
      "end_time": 174540.0,
      "text": "helped me move beyond the darkness and the guilt"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 174564.0,
      "end_time": 177452.0,
      "text": "associated with the worst moment of my young life."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 178250.0,
      "end_time": 179875.0,
      "text": "It gave me a sense that I was useful."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 180758.0,
      "end_time": 182742.0,
      "text": "She was 13 years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 183156.0,
      "end_time": 185704.0,
      "text": "She had wrote that she saw me as a hero."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 186318.0,
      "end_time": 187706.0,
      "text": "I remember reading that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 187730.0,
      "end_time": 190457.0,
      "text": "and I remember crying when I read those words."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 191234.0,
      "end_time": 193678.0,
      "text": "She was one of over 50 students"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 193702.0,
      "end_time": 197752.0,
      "text": "and 150 letters that I wrote during a mentoring correspondence program"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 197776.0,
      "end_time": 199386.0,
      "text": "that I co-designed with a friend"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 199410.0,
      "end_time": 201740.0,
      "text": "who was a teacher at a middle school in Brooklyn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 201764.0,
      "end_time": 202920.0,
      "text": "my hometown."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 202944.0,
      "end_time": 205000.0,
      "text": "We called it the Young Scholars Program."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 205693.0,
      "end_time": 209415.0,
      "text": "Every time those young people shared their stories with me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 209439.0,
      "end_time": 211460.0,
      "text": "their struggles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 211700.0,
      "end_time": 214843.0,
      "text": "every time they drew a picture of their favorite cartoon character"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 214867.0,
      "end_time": 216302.0,
      "text": "and sent it to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 216326.0,
      "end_time": 220696.0,
      "text": "every time they said they depended on my letters or my words of advice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 220720.0,
      "end_time": 222619.0,
      "text": "it boosted my sense of worthiness."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 223661.0,
      "end_time": 226736.0,
      "text": "It gave me a sense of what I could contribute to this planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 227328.0,
      "end_time": 228773.0,
      "text": "It transformed my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 229368.0,
      "end_time": 232266.0,
      "text": "Because of those letters and what they shared with me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 232290.0,
      "end_time": 234155.0,
      "text": "their stories of teen life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 234179.0,
      "end_time": 236249.0,
      "text": "they gave me the permission,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 236273.0,
      "end_time": 238689.0,
      "text": "they gave me the courage to admit to myself"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 238713.0,
      "end_time": 241516.0,
      "text": "that there were reasons -- not excuses --"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 241540.0,
      "end_time": 245953.0,
      "text": "but that there were reasons for that fateful day in October of 1999;"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 246617.0,
      "end_time": 249259.0,
      "text": "that the trauma associated with living in a community"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 249283.0,
      "end_time": 251457.0,
      "text": "where guns are easier to get than sneakers;"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 252612.0,
      "end_time": 258630.0,
      "text": "that the trauma associated with being raped at gunpoint at the age of 14;"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 259427.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262124.00000000003,
      "text": "that those are reasons for me"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 262148.0,
      "end_time": 263938.0,
      "text": "why making that decision,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 263962.0,
      "end_time": 265127.0,
      "text": "that fatal decision,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 265151.0,
      "end_time": 267115.0,
      "text": "was not an unlikely proposition."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 268120.0,
      "end_time": 270719.0,
      "text": "Because those letters mattered so much to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 270743.0,
      "end_time": 272151.0,
      "text": "because writing and receiving"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 272175.0,
      "end_time": 274432.0,
      "text": "and having that communication with those folks"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 274456.0,
      "end_time": 275955.0,
      "text": "so hugely impacted my life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 275979.0,
      "end_time": 278861.0,
      "text": "I decided to share the opportunity with some friends of mine"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 278885.0,
      "end_time": 280281.0,
      "text": "who were also inside with me."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 280305.0,
      "end_time": 282262.0,
      "text": "My friends Bill and Cory and Arocks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 282286.0,
      "end_time": 284510.0,
      "text": "all in prison for violent crimes also,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 284534.0,
      "end_time": 287337.0,
      "text": "shared their words of wisdom with the young people as well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 287362.0,
      "end_time": 289623.0,
      "text": "and received the sense of relevancy in return."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 290142.0,
      "end_time": 293328.0,
      "text": "We are now published writers and youth program innovators"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 293352.0,
      "end_time": 295101.0,
      "text": "and trauma experts"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 295125.0,
      "end_time": 296994.0,
      "text": "and gun violence prevention advocates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 297180.0,
      "end_time": 298395.0,
      "text": "and TED talkers and --"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 298420.0,
      "end_time": 299446.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 299470.0,
      "end_time": 300924.0,
      "text": "and good daddies."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 300948.0,
      "end_time": 303763.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what I call a positive return of investment."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 304570.0,
      "end_time": 305719.0,
      "text": "Above all else,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 305744.0,
      "end_time": 309647.0,
      "text": "what building that program taught me was that when we sow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 309671.0,
      "end_time": 313433.0,
      "text": "when we invest in the humanity of people no matter where they&#39;re at,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 313457.0,
      "end_time": 315921.0,
      "text": "we can reap amazing rewards."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 316811.0,
      "end_time": 319145.0,
      "text": "In this latest era of criminal justice reform,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 319170.0,
      "end_time": 322940.0,
      "text": "I often question and wonder why --"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 322812.0,
      "end_time": 324345.0,
      "text": "why is it that so many believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 324369.0,
      "end_time": 327835.0,
      "text": "that only those who have been convicted of nonviolent drug offenses"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 327859.0,
      "end_time": 331669.0,
      "text": "merit empathy and recognized humanity?"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 332908.0,
      "end_time": 335385.0,
      "text": "Criminal justice reform is human justice."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 335813.0,
      "end_time": 337288.0,
      "text": "Am I not human?"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 338700.0,
      "end_time": 343178.0,
      "text": "When we invest in resources that amplify the relevancy of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 343202.0,
      "end_time": 344672.0,
      "text": "in communities like Laventille"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 344696.0,
      "end_time": 346845.0,
      "text": "or parts of Brooklyn or a ghetto near you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 346869.0,
      "end_time": 349541.0,
      "text": "we can literally create the communities that we want."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 350440.0,
      "end_time": 351423.0,
      "text": "We can do better."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 351447.0,
      "end_time": 355350.0,
      "text": "We can do better than investing solely in law enforcement as a resource,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 355590.0,
      "end_time": 357956.0,
      "text": "because they don&#39;t give us a sense of relevancy"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 357980.0,
      "end_time": 361530.0,
      "text": "that is at the core of why so many of us do so many harmful things"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 361554.0,
      "end_time": 364226.0,
      "text": "in the pursuit of mattering."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 365176.0,
      "end_time": 369224.0,
      "text": "See, gun violence is just a visible display of a lot of underlying traumas."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 370263.0,
      "end_time": 373294.0,
      "text": "When we invest in the redemptive value of relevancy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 373319.0,
      "end_time": 377711.0,
      "text": "we can render a return of both personal responsibility and healing."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 378124.0,
      "end_time": 380368.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the people work I care about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 380392.0,
      "end_time": 381824.0,
      "text": "because people work."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 383133.0,
      "end_time": 387610.0,
      "text": "Family, I&#39;m asking you to do the hard work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 387850.0,
      "end_time": 388532.0,
      "text": "the difficult work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 388557.0,
      "end_time": 391492.0,
      "text": "the churning work of bestowing undeserved kindness"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 391516.0,
      "end_time": 393963.0,
      "text": "upon those who we can relegate as garbage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 393987.0,
      "end_time": 396155.0,
      "text": "who we can disregard and discard easily."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 396843.0,
      "end_time": 398169.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m asking myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 399330.0,
      "end_time": 401250.0,
      "text": "Over the past two months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 401274.0,
      "end_time": 403368.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve lost two friends to gun violence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 403961.0,
      "end_time": 405659.0,
      "text": "both innocent bystanders."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 406748.0,
      "end_time": 409835.0,
      "text": "One was caught in a drive-by while walking home."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 410920.0,
      "end_time": 414330.0,
      "text": "The other was sitting in a café while eating breakfast,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 414570.0,
      "end_time": 415758.0,
      "text": "while on vacation in Miami."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 417595.0,
      "end_time": 420913.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m asking myself to see the redemptive value of relevancy"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 420937.0,
      "end_time": 422639.0,
      "text": "in the people that murdered them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 423519.0,
      "end_time": 426140.0,
      "text": "because of the hard work of seeing the value in me."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 426671.0,
      "end_time": 430805.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m pushing us to challenge our own capacity"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 430829.0,
      "end_time": 433194.0,
      "text": "to fully experience our humanity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 433218.0,
      "end_time": 435207.0,
      "text": "by understanding the full biography"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 435231.0,
      "end_time": 438276.0,
      "text": "of people who we can easily choose not to see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 439728.0,
      "end_time": 442945.0,
      "text": "because heroes are waiting to be recognized,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 442969.0,
      "end_time": 444805.0,
      "text": "and music is waiting to be made."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 445656.0,
      "end_time": 446924.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 446948.0,
      "end_time": 450885.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}